\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.1}{\ignorespaces ANON4REID evaluation pipeline. Each anonymized dataset variant is evaluated for both utility (OSNet \acrshort {reid} performance) and privacy (MobileNetV2 attacker accuracy).}}{6}{figure.caption.5}%
